For what you get I dont think its worth the inflated prices they try to charge.	For those who have had complaints, I think that you should consider the value of a place that puts you in the heart of everything and offers a great nights rest in rooms that are comfortable and clean.	Sure, the Grand isn't anything overly special, but it's a great hotel for its price.	I was also lucky to get the room at a great price since it was early June and I booked it a while ago.	I've stayed at this hotel three years in a row now, mostly because of the price.